Unique fund code or symbol, usually we display this code on frontend.
The percentage of the fund's assets invested in preferred stocks. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in emerging Asian markets, such as China, India, Indonesia, Cambodia, Malaysia, Philippines, Thailand, Vietnam and other emerging Aisan countries. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in developed Asian markets, such as Brunei, French Polynesia, Guam, Hong Kong, Macau, New Caledonia, Singapore, South Korea, Taiwan. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)
The percentage of the fund's equity investments in utility sector. This sector includes electric, gas, and water utilities. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in technology sector.This sector includes companies that engaged in the design, development, and support of computer operating systems and applications, provide computer technology consulting services and companies engaged in the manufacturing of computer equipment, data storage products, networking products, semiconductors, and components. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)
The percentage of the fund's equity investments in real estate sector. This sector includes mortgage companies, property management companies, and REITs. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in industrials sector. This sector includes manufacture machinery, hand-held tools, industrial products, aerospace and defense firms as well as companies engaged in transportation and logistic services. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in healthcare sector. This sector includes biotechnology, pharmaceuticals, research services, home healthcare, hospitals, long-term-care facilities, and medical equipment and supplies. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in financial services sector. This sector includes banks, savings and loans, asset management companies, credit services, investment brokerage firms, and insurance companies. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in energy sector. This sector includes companies engaged in the mining of coal, produce or refine oil and gas, oil field services and equipment companies, and pipeline operators.  Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in communication services sector. This sector includes companies that provide internet services such as access, navigation, and internet-related software and services. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in consumer defensive sector. This sector includes companies that engaged in the manufacturing of food, beverages, household and personal products, packaging, or tobacco and provide services such as education and training services. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in consumer cyclical sector. This sector includes retail stores, auto and auto parts manufacturers, companies engaged in residential construction, lodging facilities, restaurants, and entertainment companies. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)

The percentage of the fund's equity investments in basic materials sector. Companies that manufacture chemicals, building materials and paper products. This sector also includes companies engaged in commodities exploration and processing. Value is in decimal (e.g. 23.15)
